                                                                            <comments>
                            <comment id="452727" author="adilger" created="Wed, 16 Apr 2025 16:47:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The &lt;a href=&quot;https://wiki.lustre.org/images/d/d0/LUG2025-NCSA_Lustre_Site_Update-Maloney.pdf&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;NCSA LUG presentation&lt;/a&gt; reports using a default &lt;tt&gt;max-inherit-rr=10&lt;/tt&gt; with their 48-MDT Delta filesystem to provide good MDT space balance (45/48 MDTs are within 6% usage of each other).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The &lt;a href=&quot;https://wiki.lustre.org/images/f/f9/LUG2025-Lustre_DNE3-Busting_the_Small_Files_Myth-Crusan.pdf&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;HRT LUG presentation&lt;/a&gt;  reports using &lt;tt&gt;max-inherit-rr=17&lt;/tt&gt; for each of the project directories on their 40-MDT filesystem and maintain MDT balance within 3% usage.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Conversely, we have seen imbalanced MDT usage on smaller clusters using only the &lt;tt&gt;max-inherit-rr=3&lt;/tt&gt; setting.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
